│  ├── Personal Relationship Models                             │
│  ├── Domain Expertise Accumulation                            │
│  ├── Behavioral Pattern Libraries                             │
│  └── Life Event Timeline                                      │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  📖 Episodic Memory (Experience Storage)                      │
│  ├── Conversation Archives                                    │
